Namespace EasyXLS.Constants

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alignment
    This class contains the constants for vertical and horizontal text alignment when formatting cells.
    Border
    This class contains the constants for borderline styles when formatting cells.
    Chart
    This class contains the constants used for creating charts.
    ConditionalFormatting
    This class contains the constants used for creating a conditional formatting cell range.
    DataGroup
    This class contains the constants for data grouping.
    DataType
    This class contains the constants for allowable cell data types.
    DataValidator
    This class contains the constants for creating a data validator
    Encrypt
    This class contains the constants for available encryption types.
    ErrorType
    This class contains the constants for possible errors.
    FileProperty
    This class contains the constants for the file properties of the Excel document.
    Fill
    This class contains the constants for fill effects when formatting cells.
    FontSettings
    This class contains the constants for the font underline style.
    Footer
    This class contains the allowable footer positions relative to page margins.
    Format
    This class contains the constants for number and date format when formatting cells.
    Header
    This class contains the allowable header positions relative to page margins.
    HyperlinkType
    This class contains the hyperlink type constants
    PageSetup
    This class contains the constants for page orientation, paper size, print comments options and page order when setting Page Setup options.
    Pattern
    This class contains the constants for the pattern style.
    PivotTable
    This class contains the constants for the pivot tables.
    Styles
    This class contains predefined styles for formatting cells.
    Table
    This class contains the constants for table (grid).
    Theme
    This class contains predefined themes for the document.
